OL,3,CLovers jailed for plotting to kill
OL,4,Chusband so they could continue affair
OL,6,FA woman and her lover have been jailed
OL,7,Ffor plotting to murder her husband.
OL,9,FEthel Michelle Mills, 46, known as
OL,10,FMichelle, had been having an affair
OL,11,Fwith 46-year-old Geraint Berry.
OL,12,FTogether, they plotted to murder her
OL,13,Fhusband Christopher Mills and make his
OL,14,Fdeath look like a suicide.
OL,16,FBoth were found guilty following a two-
OL,17,Fweek trial, which heard they had
OL,18,Fhatched the plan so they could
OL,19,Fcontinue their affair, and have now
OL,20,Fbeen sentenced to 19 years in prison
OL,21,Feach.
