OL,6,FMrs Mills and her husband had been at
OL,7,Ftheir caravan in Cenarth, Ceredigion,
OL,8,Fin September 2024 when two masked men
OL,9,Fwho had cable ties, gas masks and
OL,10,Fimitation firearms burst in and
OL,11,Fassaulted Mr Mills.
OL,13,FDespite being badly beaten, he fought
OL,14,Foff the intruders, who fled the
OL,15,Fcaravan park and were found hiding in
OL,16,Fnearby bushes by a police helicopter.
