OL,6,FWhile searching the pair, police found
OL,7,Fgas masks and a fake suicide note
OL,8,Faddressed to Mrs Mills purporting to
OL,9,Fhave been written by her husband. It
OL,10,Fhad DNA on the seal which matched Mrs
OL,11,FMills' DNA.
OL,13,FPolice found that she was aware that
OL,14,Fthe ambush would take place, and had
OL,15,Fplayed an integral part in conspiring
OL,16,Fto murder her husband.
OL,18,FDyfed-Powys Police said the couple had
OL,19,Fpreviously discussed using gas to kill
OL,20,FMr Mills, while making it look like he
OL,21,Fhad taken his own life.
