OL,6,FDetective Inspector Sam Gregory said:
OL,7,F"No explanation has been given by any
OL,8,Fof the three defendants for the fake
OL,9,Fsuicide note or the gas masks in the
OL,10,Frucksack. What's clear is that these
OL,11,Fwere not being used to frighten Mr
OL,12,FMills ` they were there to set up a
OL,13,Ffake suicide."
