OL,6,FDigital forensic work uncovered
OL,7,Fmessages between Mrs Mills and Berry
OL,8,Fmaking reference to ways in which they
OL,9,Fcould kill her husband, with
OL,10,Finvestigators finding messages dated
OL,11,Fthe previous month saying that Mr
OL,12,FMills "should just die".
OL,14,FThe couple had been discussing ways in
OL,15,Fwhich Berry could plan a "hit" on Mr
OL,16,FMills, with his wife saying she wished
OL,17,Fshe could poison her husband with
OL,18,Fsleeping tablets, while Berry started
OL,19,Fmaking arrangements for someone to
OL,20,Fshoot him.
