OL,6,FHe sent messages to a contact
OL,7,Fenquiring about a gun with a
OL,8,Fsuppressor, and queried how to make a
OL,9,FMini Cooper S - the car being driven
OL,10,Fby the victim - explode on starting.
OL,12,FWhen Berry told Mrs Mills he was going
OL,13,Fto meet with some "boys" to plan "what
OL,14,Fthey are going to do with him", she
OL,15,Fresponded: "Yes, lovely, thank you".
OL,17,FWhen Mrs Mills was arrested, she told
OL,18,Fofficers: "I'm going to prison for
OL,19,Fthis, aren't I?"
