OL,6,FDI Gregory said: "The communication
OL,7,Fbetween Mills and Berry that we were
OL,8,Fable to retrieve made it clear that
OL,9,Fsince the end of June 2024, the pair
OL,10,Fhad embarked on a secret relationship.
OL,11,FIn a short period of time, Berry,
OL,12,Fencouraged by Mills, became
OL,13,Fincreasingly occupied by hostile
OL,14,Fthoughts about her husband, and the
OL,15,Fpair had communicated a number of ways
OL,16,Fin which they could kill him. Despite
OL,17,Fthese conversations, Mills claimed she
OL,18,Fthought these plans were just fantasy
OL,19,Fand that their ideas would never be
OL,20,Facted on."
