OL,6,FMichelle Mills, from Llangennach,
OL,7,FCarmarthenshire, was jailed for 19
OL,8,Fyears for conspiracy to murder, and
OL,9,Fgiven an 18-month sentence to run
OL,10,Fconcurrently for perverting the course
OL,11,Fof justice.
OL,13,FBerry, from Clydach, Swansea, was
OL,14,Fconvicted of conspiracy to murder, for
OL,15,Fwhich he received a 19-year prison
OL,16,Fsentence, and pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fpossession of an imitation firearm
OL,18,Fwith intent to cause fear of violence,
OL,19,Ffor which he was given an 18-month
OL,20,Fsentence to run concurrently.
