OL,6,FDI Gregory said: "While this case has
OL,7,Fall the makings of a TV drama, at the
OL,8,Fheart of it was a very real conspiracy
OL,9,Fto take someone's life, and there were
OL,10,Fpotentially fatal consequences to the
OL,11,Fplanned attack on September 20. Mills
OL,12,Fand Barry had plotted not one, not
OL,13,Ftwo, but three attempts to take Mr
OL,14,FMills' life, and I have no doubt that
OL,15,Fthey would have continued to come up
OL,16,Fwith these plans had they not been
OL,17,Fcaught that night."
