OL,6,FGeorgia Jones, senior prosecutor at
OL,7,FCrown Prosecution Service Cymru-Wales,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a devious, callous and
OL,9,Fmurderous plot devised by a wife and
OL,10,Fher lover to kill her husband. The
OL,11,Fevidence painted a clear picture,
OL,12,Fshowing that the two defendants had
OL,13,Fbeen discussing different ways of
OL,14,Fkilling Mr Mills over the weeks
OL,15,Fleading up to the attack.
